{"tid":2223611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暴動罪存在本身就係問題，然後班人就淨係識爭議自己係咪暴動","createTime":"2020-09-30T03:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T04:22:52.000Z","uid":261647,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9a17e4189756788436b5f368a1b5ca14c59b045d","tid":2223611,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158597190927357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10158597190927357&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=4957ccd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158597190927357</a><br />\n<br />\n暴動罪存在本身就係問題，然後班人就淨係識爭議自己係咪暴動；國安法存在本身就係問題，然後班人就話自己無分裂國家。<br />\n<br />\n就算政府乜都唔做，大家已經自動向後退，又，就算向後退，政府都唔會放過你，除非你堅持「我後退左政府都唔放過我正衰人」，得，咁的確係證據。<br />\n<br />\n可惜係證明之前大家已經知，同證明係山係石頭海係水無乜分別。"},{"pid":"ec1e23b431a1eb23e3063e4613e685cd2925f870","tid":2223611,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53aaf076ce7a73ad7f9164b60d5a045f0e60894a","tid":2223611,"uid":118120,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:24:09.000Z","msg":"而家根本就係有個大隻佬企o係你面前,<br />\n求其屈個罪名俾你 ,  唔推翻佢你係唔會 Justify 到自己<br />\n因為人地從頭到尾係用拳頭逼你就範, 唔係用道理"},{"pid":"02a104cf363e72acd5e85ecc4b8f196321eb932c","tid":2223611,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T03:27:51.000Z","msg":"係賊黨面前講訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我不嬲支持走得就走"},{"pid":"2741a7deccbb94c12659552d62c37cd734c64f0f","tid":2223611,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0